flowchart TB
    FE(["Frontend<br/>TanStack Query"]) -->|HTTP request| API["Backend API Route"]

    API --> ZOD["Zod validate request"]
    ZOD -->|valid| CACHE{"Upstash cache hit?"}
    ZOD -->|invalid| ERR["Return 400 error"]

    %% CACHE HIT
    CACHE -->|Yes| CACHED["Return cached data"]
    CACHED --> FE

    %% BACKGROUND REFRESH
    CACHED --> BG["Trigger background refresh"]
    BG --> LINEAR["Fetch data from Linear API"]
    LINEAR --> MAP["Map and normalize data"]
    MAP --> ZOD_RES["Zod validate response"]
    ZOD_RES -->|valid| UPDATE["Update Upstash cache"]
    ZOD_RES -->|invalid| LOG["Log error"]

    %% CACHE MISS
    CACHE -->|No| LINEAR
    SAVE --> FE

    %% TANSTACK QUERY POLLING
    FE -.->|refetch after first data arrives | API


    style B stroke-width:4px,stroke-dasharray: 0